| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1049 — Mass File Rename (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 59118c0b-29f2-5d88-afe5-184579366256"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
